	<h2>Discover LaTeX &mdash; the professional typesetting system</h2>

	<p>LaTeX is a markup language used to prepare documents which look
	profesionnals. It's mostly used by mathematicians, scientists,
	engineers and people from academic world and from industry. That
	training, divided in two parts, allows you to discover the LaTeX
	language.</p>

	<p>The practical sessions will, as the theoretical course, be given in
	<strong>French</strong> by mentors.</p>

	<ul>
		<li>First part consists in <strong>a &laquo; theoretical &raquo;
		course</strong> presenting the basis of LaTeX. This
		part introduce you to what is possible to do using LaTeX,
		in particular we saw how to include graphics, arrays,
		mathematics, code... You can download the slides&nbsp;<a
		href="/slides/formation-latex.pdf">here</a>.</li>
		
		<li>Second part consists in <strong>practical sessions</strong>
		on computer. In this part, you will be in front of a computer
		and will be asked to produce documents with LaTeX.  Several
		sessions from different levels are organised: from complete
		beginner to more advanced. The practical sessions are
		supervised by tutors.</li>
	</ul>

